== 拍攝 ==
《成人世界》是導演[[尼爾·布洛姆坎普|尼爾·布洛姆坎普]]所執導的第三部長片，他與一同為《[[第九禁區|第九禁區]]》編劇的妻子{{link-en|泰芮·塔契爾|Terri Tatchell}}再次負責本片的劇本。電影於2013年10月中在[[南非|南非]]的[[約翰內斯堡|約翰內斯堡]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Neill Blomkamp's Chappie Starts Filming, Adds Sigourney Weaver|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=110711|accessdate=2013-10-29|newspaper=comingsoon.net|date=2013-10-28|archive-date=2014-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141018110147/http://www.comingsoon.net/news/movienews.php?id=110711|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Production Begins on Blomkamp's 'Chappie,' Adds Sigourney Weaver|url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2013/production-begins-on-blomkamps-chappie-adds-sigourney-weaver/|accessdate=2013-10-29|newspaper=firstshowing.net|date=2013-10-28|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329103757/https://www.firstshowing.net/2013/production-begins-on-blomkamps-chappie-adds-sigourney-weaver/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2014年2月宣布殺青<ref>{{cite news|title=so we just finished shooting our CHAPPIE movie!|url=http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10151811205876971&set=a.81773461970.90028.80749331970&type=1|accessdate=2014-11-05|archive-date=2019-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403074915/https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10151811205876971&set=a.81773461970.90028.80749331970&type=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

